muxi.payservices.service

Class MPSManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • muxi.payservices.service.MPSManager

  • public class MPSManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for communication with muxiPAY services. It sends the command to start service, stop service, init muxiPAY services and make payment. It is also is this class that is receipt the answer from service about success or errors of these commands.
